trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry" /> creates or removes a user inclusion list entry at build time for application-level add-ins and document-level customizations in the 2007 Microsoft Office system.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry" /> 在生成时针对 2007 Microsoft Office 系统中的应用程序级外接程序和文档级自定义创建或删除用户包含列表条目。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: Set all of the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry> properties, and then call <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute%2A> to run this build task.
trans-unit.target: 设置所有<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry>属性，，然后调用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute%2A>运行此生成任务。

trans-unit.source: The Microsoft Build Engine uses <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks> to build and deploy Office solutions.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft Build Engine 使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks>生成和部署 Office 解决方案。

trans-unit.source: However, you can create your own build system by using these classes and the MSBuild XML-based project files.
trans-unit.target: 但是，可以使用这些类并基于 MSBuild XML 项目文件来创建你自己生成系统。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [MSBuild Reference](~/msbuild/msbuild-reference.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[MSBuild 参考](~/msbuild/msbuild-reference.md)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The following table shows initial property values for an instance of the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry> class.
trans-unit.target: 下表显示了 <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry> 类的某个实例的初始属性值。

trans-unit.source: Property
trans-unit.target: Property

trans-unit.source: Initial Value
trans-unit.target: 初始值

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the certificate thumbprint.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置证书指纹。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the certificate thumbprint.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.String" />表示的证书指纹。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the fully qualified path of the deployment manifest.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置部署清单的绝对路径。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the fully qualified path of the deployment manifest.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.String" />表示部署清单的完全限定的路径。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.DeploymentManifestFullPath%2A> property must be assigned before <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.DeploymentManifestFullPath%2A>属性必须之前分配<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: Creates or removes a record in a user inclusion list at build time for application-level add-ins and document-level customizations.
trans-unit.target: 在生成时针对应用程序级外接程序和文档级自定义创建或删除用户包含列表中的记录。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the inclusion list entry was created or removed successfully; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果成功创建或删除包含列表条目，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether to remove the inclusion list entry.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示是否删除包含列表条目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see cref="M:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute" /> removes the inclusion list entry; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 如果<see cref="M:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Office.BuildTasks.SetInclusionListEntry.Execute" />移除包含列表项; 否则为<see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="false" />。
